Package suncertify.db

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BookingDB
    An extended version of the DB interface to provide specific functionality required for the URLyBird Application.
    DB
    Interface for URLyBird application as supplied.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BookingData
    Implementation of the BookingDB interface for the URLyBird Application.
    BookingDataProxy
    This class provides a proxy so that classes can access data across the network transparently as if they were using a non-networked data access object that implements the BookingDB interface.
    BookingDBFactory
    This factory class is used to make instances of classes that implement the BookingDB interface.
    Data
    Database access class for the URLyBird application.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicateKeyException
    DuplicateKeyException is thrown if an attempt to create a duplicate record is made.
    InvalidDataFileException
    This exception is thrown if the data file being read by a Data object does not have the correct format.
    RecordNotFoundException
    This exception is thrown if the Record requested does not exist or is deleted.
    SecurityException
    SecurityException is thrown if an incorrect lock cookie is supplied when calling a method that requires a record to be locked first.
